reviewText:
Besides unfixed bugs like:

• Internet Cafe's owners spawnning together in the same spot;
• Dating one of the girls (Alex) is not working correctly, so your dates always fail;
• A glitch disables Wanted Level so you can end the game without worrying about the police;
• Manhunt achievement not working;
• Random crashes, like when you perform a benchmark test or ride a cab.

I DO RECOMMEND THIS GAME. Well, as long as you can deal with these problems.

PS: I know some players have not experienced such bugs. I don't care: if I did, someone else may experience them as well. So I'm giving Rockstar a thumbs down until them address these problems.
